      <title>喜力啤酒因中美贸易战而收取 9.49 亿美元费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/heineken-takes-nearly-1b-one-off-china-charge-narrows-guidance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国这一关键市场以及美国的消费支出面临压力，喜力啤酒公司 (Heineken NV) 因其所持中国最大啤酒制造商的股份估值下降而计提了 8.74 亿欧元（9.49 亿美元）的减值准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/heineken-takes-nearly-1b-one-off-china-charge-narrows-guidance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:23:36 GMT</pubDate>
