    <item>
      <title>酿酒商欧元上涨，汽车制造商萎靡不振：欧洲、中东和非洲地区本周财报展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/brewers-get-euros-kick-carmakers-wilt-emea-earnings-week-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[喜力啤酒公司 (Heineken NV) 周一公布了令人失望的第二季度业绩，凸显了啤酒制造商面临的挑战，而其比利时竞争对手百威英博 (Anheuser-Busch Inbev) 也准备在本周晚些时候公布业绩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/brewers-get-euros-kick-carmakers-wilt-emea-earnings-week-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
